    "description": "Gavin Tyler's Game Collection is a collection of old games released by Gavin Tyler. It goes from his earliest work to his newest. Some games are bad, while some games are good. There are 7 games in total!<br><br><strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >GAMES LIST:</h2></strong><br><br><strong>- Rage Game: The Game</strong><br>The first game released by Gavin Tyler! Can you finish all levels without dying?<br><br><strong>- Rage Game: The Game Cancelled Demo</strong><br>A &quot;polished&quot; version of the original Rage Game: The Game, with one large level!<br><br><strong>- Room Service</strong><br>A jam game for &quot;Secret Santa Jam&quot;. You work as a janitor at a sketchy hotel!<br><br><strong>- Passageways 3D</strong><br>A roguelike horror game about endless passageways. How long can you survive until the comic monsters catch you?<br><br><strong>- Passageways 3D Dev Version</strong><br>A developer version of Passageways 3D. This is the first time it is being publicly released!<br><br><strong>- Bus Survivalist</strong><br>Originally made as a joke, Bus Survivalist is a game about trying to withstand a bus ride to school. The catch? It's the elementary bus!<br><br><strong>- Gavin's Wonderhouse</strong><br>Gavin's Wonderhouse is a parody of the typical mascot horror game. Grab all the birthday cake you can before getting caught by Gavin!",
